ygData.messageBody:
Most of the time pple are nice enuff to bind or SoW for free, and donation
is optional. If anyone ask for a fee, ask them go fly kites, unless u at
wulu wulu place where u can't find anyone to help u ;)

I died twice on a row yesterday at west common, and there is a Druid with
name Morxxxxx SoW twice at west gate. When I get back my corpse and gate
back to west gate, I pay him some money. Leshrec can bind liao at lvl 15.
He always go for those chim chim wulu wulu place. I'm still 3 bubb to lvl
12 b4 I can bind, and I stay around Freeport, Ecommon & Wcommon. Once I
can bind, we got 2 binders in local community liao ;)

Ziltus
